    "content": "---\r\ntags:\r\n  - \"#diagram\"\r\ntype: \"flowchart|sequence|class|er|gantt|mindmap|state\"\r\ntopic: \"\"\r\n---\r\n# Diagram: Topic Name\r\n\r\nBrief description of what this diagram shows.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n```mermaid\r\nflowchart TD\r\n    A[Start] --> B{Decision}\r\n    B -->|Yes| C[Do this]\r\n    B -->|No| D[Do that]\r\n    C --> E[End]\r\n    D --> E\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## Notes\r\n- What the diagram represents\r\n- Key components explained\r\n- [[Related Note]]\r\n",
